Guard- (6)
- The guard provides strong protection to 1 user at a time.
-- If the Guard's target is weak or strong attacked, The guard will die and the attack will fail.
-- If the Guard's target is attacked using an unstoppable attack, both the guard and the target will die.
-- When the guard dies instead of its target, the killers visit is not redirected into having visited the guard.
- They cannot change their target after initially picking it (Unless the target somehow dies before the guard).
- The guard cannot be role-blocked. The guard is the last layer of protection, any other protection will be used before this.
- Action is night end. Counts as a visiting action.
- Respawns in 4 phases.
